.row
  .span7
    - set_title @group.name, "", @group.parent
    = render '/groups/title', group: @group
.row.iconrow
  .span2
    = image_tag "loomio-users.png"
  .span7
    %h1 You choose how much to pay
.row
  .span7.offset2
    %p
      Groups with a budget typically choose a monthly rate of about
      %span $2 - $5 per person.
    %p
      %em (e.g. business, government, community orgs)

    %p
      If your group is flat broke, you can even
      %span
        choose $0!
.row.iconrow
  .span2
    = image_tag "colablove.png", id: 'colablove'
  .span5
    %h2 Set your group subscription:
    %label.radio.notzero
      = radio_button_tag "subs", 100
      $100 per month
    %label.radio.notzero
      = radio_button_tag "subs", 50
      $50 per month
    %label.radio.notzero
      = radio_button_tag "subs", 25
      $25 per month
    %label.radio.notzero
      = radio_button_tag "subs", 10
      $10 per month
    %label.radio.notzero
      = radio_button_tag "subs", "other"
      Choose another amount:
      .input-prepend
        %span.add-on= '$'
        %input.input-mini{:id => "custom_amount", :name => "subs", :type => "text"}
    %label.radio.zero
      = radio_button_tag "subs", 0
      $0 per month
    #lovenote
      ♥ We'll still love you, even if you can't afford a group subscription. We'll occasionally ask your group members for a voluntary individual contribution. ♥

    %input{type: 'submit', value: "Pay now with Paypal", class: "btn btn-success btn-block btn-large"}


    %p.later
      =link_to "Ask me later", "#"

    %p.small Amounts are in USD. You can change your payment at any time.
